Package: hierCP
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Changepoints and Forecast Reconciliation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Benedict", family = "Debrah", email = "benedictdebrah.o@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Tools for hierarchical changepoint detection (independent, top-down, bottom-up), 
    windowed optimal partition with basic PELT-style pruning, base forecasting via GM(1,1) or ARIMA, 
    and coherent forecast reconciliation with simple structured regularization.
